who was playing tennis

15:59.421 --> 16:01.322
With rachel maddow--
i hate to admit it,

16:01.390 --> 16:04.292
But the lesbians count--
la maddow is a huge adele fan.

16:04.359 --> 16:07.995
Voilá, winning y.e.t.i. project!
doo doo doo doo doo!
yay!

16:08.046 --> 16:10.014
