16:36.141 --> 16:40.661
Look, we'll figure
something out.
it is too late.
lives are at stake.

16:40.712 --> 16:42.914
We are voting him
off the island.

16:42.998 --> 16:44.882
He is the weakest link!
shh!

16:44.967 --> 16:47.468
Auf wiedersehen! that's it!
good-bye! he's fired.

16:47.536 --> 16:49.704
Um, i-i can hear you,
you know.
that was the point!

16:49.755 --> 16:51.722
