for dramatic effect.

16:51.807 --> 16:54.976
Do, uh, do you want
to fire me, too?

16:55.027 --> 16:56.961
No.

16:57.029 --> 16:59.964
But, matt, this is
really important to us,

17:00.048 --> 17:02.483
And i know how capable
you are.

17:02.551 --> 17:04.452
But for whatever reason,

17:04.520 --> 17:06.887
It just seems like
you don't care.

17:06.954 --> 17:09.190
You're right.

17:09.241 --> 17:11.375
You're, uh,
absolutely right.

17:11.460 --> 17:14.145
