a happy wedding dress.
she looks like
a baboon's ass.

19:51.604 --> 19:54.406
She didn't mean that.
oh, stop talking
to the props, amateur.

19:54.491 --> 19:57.409
Would anyone like
a nice, warm scone?
you might not remember
your wedding

19:57.477 --> 19:59.428
Because it was
5,000 years ago,

19:59.495 --> 20:01.764
But when i married your husband,
it was all about class.

20:01.815 --> 20:04.450
And this dress
has none of it.
well, no wonder

20:04.534 --> 20:06.635
You prefer to put brides
in black dresses,

20:06.686 --> 20:08.804
Since you killed your groom
at the altar.

20:08.855 --> 20:10.722
(whispering) we're gonna
get you out of here.

20:10.807 --> 20:12.708
Just wait for my cue.
(sighs) take off
the dress.

