All right! all right! now!
move! move! move!

20:20.934 --> 20:22.651
Serpentine, serpentine!
you let go!

20:22.702 --> 20:25.137
Just get over here!
(grunts)

20:25.205 --> 20:27.156
(whimpers)

20:27.207 --> 20:29.191
Such a shame.

20:33.060 --> 20:36.413
Yeah, my goal is to give you
the perfect wedding,

20:36.497 --> 20:38.097
