with everyone dancing.

20:56.901 --> 21:00.403
Is this too much?
no. i want you to have
whatever you want.

21:00.488 --> 21:02.789
Well, it all looks
very doable.

21:02.840 --> 21:04.925
So what date
did you have in mind?

21:04.976 --> 21:07.127
We were kind of thinking
as soon as possible.

21:07.194 --> 21:09.079
Like--like the end
of the month.

21:09.147 --> 21:10.747
This month?
mm-hmm.

21:10.832 --> 21:12.732
Mr. meade,
a-a wedding like this

21:12.800 --> 21:15.285
