22:11.809 --> 22:13.560
Who's on the board
of the planetarium,

22:13.627 --> 22:15.579
Reminded her
of a few things i saw

22:15.663 --> 22:17.631
At last year's
christmas party...

22:17.682 --> 22:19.899
(chuckles)
and it's yours.
wow, um...

22:19.951 --> 22:22.368
Why are you doing this
for me?

22:22.420 --> 22:25.672
