about your relationship.

24:44.225 --> 24:46.127
What i care about
is my future,

24:46.194 --> 24:48.112
And if we don't have matt
in the group,

24:48.196 --> 24:50.531
Then we don't get
the planetarium,

24:50.582 --> 24:52.633
And then our entire
final project is dead.

24:52.684 --> 24:54.702
Look, we're out of options
at "mode."

24:54.769 --> 24:57.838
Just make it work.

24:57.906 --> 25:00.307
