25:03.562 --> 25:06.280
Oh! oh, i'm so sorry.
it's okay.

25:06.331 --> 25:08.382
Oh! smooth, 'nacio.

25:08.450 --> 25:12.052
Let me get that.
no, it's o--
i'll get it.

25:12.104 --> 25:13.587
