25:16.224 --> 25:19.026
I know you're considering
that job, but...

25:19.093 --> 25:20.494
I love you, elena.

25:20.545 --> 25:22.796
And i think we have
a future together.

25:22.848 --> 25:27.651
At least,
i hope we do.

25:27.719 --> 25:30.187
(sighs)

25:30.272 --> 25:32.323
Will you marry me?

25:37.145 --> 25:39.613
Oh, my god.

25:39.664 --> 25:42.266
