25:52.844 --> 25:54.912
Yes.
(laughs)

25:54.996 --> 25:56.997
Yes.

25:57.048 --> 25:59.366
Yes, yes.

25:59.417 --> 26:01.635
(both laugh)

26:03.622 --> 26:05.055
Art books.

26:05.123 --> 26:07.024
Wow.

26:07.108 --> 26:09.059
Matt, i've been thinking--

26:09.144 --> 26:11.061
And don't hate me
for saying this--

26:11.146 --> 26:14.314
But do you think maybe it would
be worth it to finish y.e.t.i.

26:14.366 --> 26:16.667
