till next week,

26:24.176 --> 26:26.944
So i just
don't see a downside.
wow, you sound
like my mother.

26:27.028 --> 26:29.947
Oh, no, no,
i'm--i'm sorry.
no, it's okay, it's okay.
somehow, coming from you,

26:30.031 --> 26:32.900
