want to break things.

26:32.968 --> 26:35.553
And maybe i was
a little... selfish,

26:35.637 --> 26:37.738
Leaving you guys
in the lurch like that.

26:37.805 --> 26:40.941
So... you'll come back?

26:40.992 --> 26:44.528
Well, when you do that cute
squinty thing with your eyes,

26:44.613 --> 26:47.665
How could i say no?
yay!

26:47.749 --> 26:50.634
And don't worry.
you're nothing like my mother.

26:56.379 --> 26:58.280
A little, uh,
a little less bouffant.

26:58.348 --> 27:00.265
We're going more, um,
'70s and '60s,

