uh-huh.

27:04.637 --> 27:07.022
Hi. you ready to go?
you're really good at this.
i'm glad you're back.

27:07.106 --> 27:09.541
Me, too. oh, uh, you know,
we need to test those lights.

27:09.609 --> 27:12.344
I don't want them to interfere.
i think they're strobing.

